<blockquote>
  <p>Gaming disorder is characterized by a pattern of persistent or recurrent gaming behaviour (â€˜digital gamingâ€™ or â€˜video-gamingâ€™), which may be online (i.e., over the internet) or offline, manifested by:</p>
